# 🍲 AI-Powered Recipe Recommendation App

An intelligent and interactive recipe app that helps users discover personalized recipes based on their preferences, ingredients, and dietary goals — powered by artificial intelligence and modern web technologies.
---

## 🧠 Features

- 🥦 Ingredient-based recipe search
- 📸 AI-generated images based on recipe titles
- 🧑‍🍳 Step-by-step cooking instructions
- 🍽️ Dynamic filtering by diet, cuisine, and meal type
- 💬 AI suggestions for similar recipes
- 🔍 Auto-fill search using popular ingredients
- 🌐 Clean, responsive UI for all devices

---

## 🔧 Tech Stack

| Layer        | Tech Used                                       |
|--------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Frontend     | HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap                 |
| Backend      | Node.js, Express.js                              |
| Database     | MongoDB (optional: switchable with PostgreSQL)   |
| APIs         | Edamam Recipe API, OpenAI / Gemini (for AI recs) |
| Image Gen    | DALL·E / AI-powered image suggestions            |

---

